</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 6:27
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='372000' id='t-372000'>Well I don't think that.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='374000' id='t-374000'>I think that Hardy had a lot going for him.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='376000' id='t-376000'>I'd like to talk about just a handful</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='379000' id='t-379000'>of what have been called the</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='381000' id='t-381000'>hallmarks of mankind,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='383000' id='t-383000'>the things that made us different from everybody else,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='385000' id='t-385000'>and all our relatives.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='387000' id='t-387000'>Let's look at our naked skin.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='391000' id='t-391000'>It's obvious that most of the things we think about</span>
