</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:11
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='416000' id='t-416000'>I suggested it and people said, &quot;No no no.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='418000' id='t-418000'>I mean, look at the elephant.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='420000' id='t-420000'>You've forgotten all about the elephant haven't you?&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='422000' id='t-422000'>So back in 1982 I said,</span>
