<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='445000' id='t-445000'>The last exception was supposed to be the rhinoceros.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 7:42
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='447000' id='t-447000'>Last year in Florida they found extinct ancestor of a rhinoceros</span>
