<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='467000' id='t-467000'>because look at the sea otter.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='469000' id='t-469000'>But you can say</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='471000' id='t-471000'>that every animal that has become naked</span>
