<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='482000' id='t-482000'>The only exception is the naked Somalian mole-rat,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='486000' id='t-486000'>which never puts its nose above the surface of the ground.</span>
