<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='520000' id='t-520000'>as the possible beginning of our bipedalism.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 8:59
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='524000' id='t-524000'>Look at the fat layer.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='526000' id='t-526000'>We have got, under our skin, a layer of fat, all over:</span>
