</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:01
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='586000' id='t-586000'>The question of why we can speak.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='588000' id='t-588000'>We can speak.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='590000' id='t-590000'>And the gorilla can't speak. Why?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='593000' id='t-593000'>Nothing to do with his teeth or his tongue or his lungs or anything like that --</span>
