<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
10:35
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='620000' id='t-620000'>And then again, there is the fact that we are streamlined.</span>
