<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='636000' id='t-636000'>we are halfway to being shaped like a fish.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='639000' id='t-639000'>I am trying to suggest that, for 40-odd years,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='642000' id='t-642000'>this aquatic idea has been miscategorized as lunatic fringe,</span>
