<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:05
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='650000' id='t-650000'>And the ironic thing about it is that</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='653000' id='t-653000'>they are not staving off the aquatic theory</span>
