<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='674000' id='t-674000'>How do they react when I say these things?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='677000' id='t-677000'>One very common reaction I've heard about 20 times</span>
