12:00
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='705000' id='t-705000'>I ask people sometimes, and they say,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='707000' id='t-707000'>&quot;I like the aquatic theory!</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='709000' id='t-709000'>Everybody likes the aquatic theory.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='711000' id='t-711000'>Of course they don't believe it, but they like it.&quot;</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='713000' id='t-713000'>Well I say, &quot;Why do you think it's rubbish?&quot;</span>
