<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='748000' id='t-748000'>(Laughter)</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:44
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='749000' id='t-749000'>Apart from that, some of the heads count more than others.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='753000' id='t-753000'>Some of them have come over.</span>
