<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:07
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='772000' id='t-772000'>And now we've got to look to the future.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='777000' id='t-777000'>Ultimately one of three things is going to happen.</span>
