<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='792000' id='t-792000'>The second thing that could happen</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='794000' id='t-794000'>is that some young genius will arrive,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='796000' id='t-796000'>and say, &quot;I've found it.</span>
