</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:42
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='807000' id='t-807000'>So the third thing that might happen is</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='810000' id='t-810000'>a very beautiful thing.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='813000' id='t-813000'>If you look back at the early years of the last century,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='816000' id='t-816000'>there was a stand-off, a lot of bickering and bad feeling</span>
