</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:54
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='879000' id='t-879000'>So if it's going to come and it's going to happen,</span>
