<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='884000' id='t-884000'>I can tell you that in three words.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='887000' id='t-887000'>Academia says no.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='891000' id='t-891000'>They decided in 1960,</span>
